yes it is an art ! greene has clearly drawn out the ways of the seducer . most of the men and women in here are naturals at seduction and are not consciously doing the principles taught . but those that tend to mess up their seductions can learn quite a few things from these people . with everything i teach at my site the seduction bible , i still believe that this book is excellent for those looking to score that one special girl . those wanting to learn how to go out to a bar to pick up a woman are better off on sites like mine . but this book deserves 5 stars